WorkItem.Description:
Would like additional samples using Event Tracing for Windows (ETW) when integrating messaging into applications that are build upon WAS (Windows Process Activation Services), WCF, WF and AppFabric. I found some examples:
http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/magazine/cc163437.aspx. I have created my own which represents an End-To-End POC, however haven't found any community samples that I could compare with.
WorkItem.Summary: Event Tracing for Windows (ETW) in AppFabric (WAS, WCF, WF, IIS)
